---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Inicio"
  description="Sistema de agendamiento de citas online. Agenda tu cita de manera fácil y rápida."
>
  <main class="relative">
    <!-- Hero section -->
    <div class="relative pt-20 pb-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="lg:mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-flow-col-dense lg:gap-24">
          <div class="px-4 max-w-xl mx-auto sm:px-6 lg:py-20 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:px-0">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-pm-gold-dim text-pm-gold border border-pm-gold/20 mb-6">
                Menos no-shows. Más ingresos para tu negocio.
              </div>
              <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-pm-text sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
                Agenda tu cita de forma
                <span class="text-pm-gold"> fácil y rápida</span>
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-pm-muted leading-relaxed">
                Agendamiento por WhatsApp con confirmaciones automáticas. Los clientes se presentan, los negocios no pierden tiempo ni dinero.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-0">
            <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-0 lg:m-0 lg:relative lg:h-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Premium calendar preview card -->
              <div class="bg-pm-surface border border-pm-border rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-premium w-full max-w-sm mx-auto">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                  <span class="text-pm-text font-semibold">Abril 2026</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-pm-gold"></div>
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-pm-border"></div>
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-pm-border"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-1 text-center text-xs text-pm-dim mb-2">
                  {["L","M","M","J","V","S","D"].map(d => <span>{d}</span>)}
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-1 text-center text-sm">
                  {[...Array(30)].map((_, i) => (
                    <span class={`py-1.5 rounded-md cursor-pointer transition-colors ${
                      i === 7 ? "bg-pm-gold text-pm-bg font-bold" :
                      [2,9,14,21].includes(i) ? "border border-pm-gold text-pm-gold" :
                      "text-pm-muted hover:bg-pm-elevated"
                    }`}>{i + 1}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-pm-border">
                  <p class="text-xs text-pm-dim mb-2">Horarios disponibles</p>
                  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    {["09:00","10:00","11:00","14:00","15:00"].map(t => (
                      <span class="px-3 py-1 border border-pm-gold text-pm-gold text-xs rounded-md">{t}</span>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- No-show stat banner -->
    <div class="border-t border-pm-border bg-pm-elevated/40">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 text-center">
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-pm-gold">↓ No-shows</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-pm-muted max-w-xs">Los clientes que agendan por WhatsApp se presentan más. El compromiso digital reduce las ausencias.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-px h-12 bg-pm-border"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-pm-gold">+ Ingresos</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-pm-muted max-w-xs">Cada cita que no se pierde es dinero que entra. Sin llamadas, sin esperas, sin huecos en la agenda.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-px h-12 bg-pm-border"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-pm-gold">24/7</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-pm-muted max-w-xs">Tu negocio recibe citas a cualquier hora, aunque estés durmiendo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature section -->
    <div class="bg-pm-surface border-t border-pm-border py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="lg:text-center">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-pm-gold font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
            Características
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-pm-text sm:text-4xl">
            Una mejor manera de gestionar tu tiempo
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-pm-gold-dim border border-pm-gold/20 text-pm-gold">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-semibold text-pm-text">Ahorra tiempo</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-pm-muted">
                Agenda tus citas en cualquier momento, sin necesidad de llamadas telefónicas.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-pm-gold-dim border border-pm-gold/20 text-pm-gold">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-semibold text-pm-text">Flexibilidad</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-pm-muted">
                Elige el horario que mejor se adapte a tu agenda.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-pm-gold-dim border border-pm-gold/20 text-pm-gold">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-semibold text-pm-text">Reduce los no-shows</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-pm-muted">
                El cliente agenda por WhatsApp y recibe confirmación al instante. Menos olvidos, menos ausencias, más ingresos para tu negocio.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-pm-gold-dim border border-pm-gold/20 text-pm-gold">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-semibold text-pm-text">Multi-proveedor</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-pm-muted">
                Gestiona múltiples proveedores y sus horarios de trabajo.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
